“fy_archplex”

This is a small sized, symmetrical Fight Yard style map. This map is also made for Gun Game play style.

- 64 Spawns
- 3d skybox
- Soundscapes
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Overview radar map
- Buy Zones
- Nav File for bots
- Pakrated

PLEASE COMMENT AND RATE THIS MAP, THANK YOU!
